00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:32.500
Lake Kournas - the only freshwater lake in Crete

00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:50.000
Lake is  located in the foothills at an altitude of 25 meters above sea level, about 40 km south-east of the city of Chania.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:03.000
The water level is constant

00:01:08.500 --> 00:01:21.200
According to legend, the lake was formed from the tears of the girl, whose name was Korisseya - so originally called this Lake

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:31.000
Later, the Arabs called it Kournas, what in Arabic means "lake"

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:37.000
On the lake you can have a excellent day

00:01:38.500 --> 00:01:41.000
 ride a pedalo

